{"tid":715971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WSJ：特朗普新計劃阻華企投資美科企 或禁技術出口","createTime":"2018-06-25T01:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T03:54:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4124797aac9f67e006f2e1af31314ea4980c9aec","tid":715971,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》引述消息報道，美國總統特朗普準備在貿易糾紛再對中國出手，新計劃將禁止「紅底」公司投資或收購美國科技企業，並阻止更多技術產品出口到中國。<br />\n<br />\n報道指美國財政部正草擬規定，禁止中國持股25%或以上的企業投資或收購美國涉「工業重要技術」的公司。有指限制並不影響已存在的華企投資業務，僅禁制華企未來的新投資，另外新限制無論是中國國營企業抑或民企也受影響。<br />\n<br />\n據報有關規定仍在討論，不排除限制或進一步擴闊至中國公司持股低於25%的公司。<br />\n<br />\n消息又指美國國家安全會議、商務部亦正草擬規定擴大對華出口科技及技術產品的限制，但未有公佈更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180625/58360002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360002&d=KGDUDqk4DuKEzo%2Bg3B1nH3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c054aa42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F58360002&h=8fea3592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180625/58360002</a>"},{"pid":"52ba28168e77370e5a3287be824cee2f4ecad92c","tid":715971,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"得返歐洲有得偷技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下幾時輪到歐洲都封殺你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5024d5373542111dc046cc48d3024f5dc1345b1","tid":715971,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52ba28168e77370e5a3287be824cee2f4ecad92c","tid":715971,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"得返歐洲有得偷技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下幾時輪到歐洲都封殺你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"偷日韓台歐加澳"}]}